The Hollaback Girl hitmaker took to TikTok over the weekend to announce that she is joining her husband Blake Shelton and fellow coach John Legend on the upcoming 22nd series. In a TikTok video, Gwen confirmed the news by singing along to Mika's Grace Kelly with Blake and John. In a separate social media post,Camila Cabello has also just been announced as the fourth coach for the new season of The Voice. Last season, Blake and John served as coaches alongside Kelly Clarkson and Ariana Grande.